<br>
Well there are different ideas on when classes are balanced. <br>
1 could be when a group would be egual efficient no matter which 6 classes there are in it, seems far out, but to some point measurable. <br>
A second oppion could be when each class would be equal good soloers, like that ever happen in a game where the designer wants to encourage grouping.<br>
Thirdly it could be when every class is needed for a raid, seems an odd way to it.<br>
<br>
Well my guess is, that none of these will never happen. There might be other ways to see when classes are balanced, but same guess from me, at the moment.<br>
<br>
Now my crazy proposal is that since it is so hard to balance the classes, it could be an idea to add xp bonus for groups to have certain classes in it, this way, some of the classes that have a hard time to find a group, would get a significant better chance in getting a group, since the group would benefit from having certain classes with and VI goals about players should group more are accomplished.<br>
<br>
